query:
SELECT se.subjectId, se.userId as professorId, s.name as subjectName
FROM subjectEnrollments se
INNER JOIN subjects s ON se.subjectId = s.id
WHERE se.studentId = (SELECT id FROM students WHERE registrationNumber = '2024001');
